  <bioghist encodinganalog="545"> 
	 <head>Historical Note</head> 
	 <p> 
	 <title render="italic">Lord of Beasts: the Saga of Buffalo Jones</title> ,
	 the story of Charles Jesse Jones, Preserver of the American Bison, was written
	 by Robert O. Easton in collaboration with Mackenzie Brown. It was published by
	 the University of Arizona Press in 1961.</p> 
  </bioghist> 
